rows.label: tlk4235012501_msg0001
rows.name:
Mokumoku impressed! Not think
anyone come looking here!

rows.label: tlk4235012501_msg0002
rows.name:
You travelers? Well, me afraid you out
of luck. Me have nothing to sell you.

rows.label: tlk4235012501_msg0003
rows.name:
Mokumoku just handle timber needed
for house and furniture building. That
not much use to travelers.

rows.label: tlk4235012501_msg0004
rows.name:
But if friends want to lug big pieces
of wood around, go ahead, be guest
of Mokumoku!
